display_long_description:
Jump into the most realistic and immersive dental simulator ever made. Every procedure hits different — one slip and your patient won’t just complain… they might sprint out of the clinic.

Master every thrilling detail:
- Dental prophylaxis cleaning and Sandbox mode available in Practice Mode.
- Administer anesthesia with pinpoint accuracy
- Cut and retract gums with skill
- Extract single or multiple teeth with finesse
- Control bleeding before it gets out of hand
- Daily randomized appointments

Go beyond the basics and push your skills further:
- Apply braces with colorful rubber bands
- Use headgear and face mask in advanced orthodontic treatments
- Craft dazzling gold and silver teeth
- Place implants like a true pro
- Keep patients calm with inhalation sedation
- And make the experience even more addictive with:
- Achievements to unlock and master
- Global leaderboards to prove who’s the #1 VR dentist
- Fun stickers to collect and share
- Lessons with real dentistry theories

With completely reworked gameplay, you have total freedom to treat each patient your way.
The pressure is real, the stakes are high — but the fun is absolutely addictive!

Download now and claim your spot as the ultimate VR dentist… just don’t let the screams get out of control!
